{"tid":1514010,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[心理]有冇恐慌症/焦慮症巴絲","createTime":"2019-08-28T14:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T11:06:31.000Z","uid":19399,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"da3a5142a5aedf1be0851f61e02cbbfe981438a6","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"八月頭突然係街心跳快到170幾<br />\n幾乎暈低，入院檢查晒話冇事住左三日就放左我出院<br />\n第四日食晏個又突然跳到160幾又送返入廠<br />\n最終係醫院訓左4,5日先有個臨床心理醫生見我<br />\n話我有恐慌症同焦慮症<br />\n長期工作壓力而成，最近兩個月又不段睇新聞，發過一次夢。<br />\n醫院個度要排到9月中先有醫生睇，現在都係無藥食每日都keep頭重重，個人浮下浮下咁。<br />\n想睇下有冇巴絲同樣有衣個病，同醫治情況係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪第一次見醫生已經會開藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲係衣段時間記得都搵野放鬆下自己，千祈唔好迫得自己太緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a84eb07598af6a737fd293577bd8d49cf5c7163f","tid":1514010,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f84020a5fe6eab86b1e81f27dcd096b7dec460e","tid":1514010,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"三年前開始睇醫生食藥 有焦慮症同驚恐症 而家無發作好耐"},{"pid":"a38784b20c0dce41b12fe6a63b9ba3ba68e23b41","tid":1514010,"uid":12348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"有無試過mediation?"},{"pid":"3814a6f2008f51fbc458e217faf2c5f65fb864f1","tid":1514010,"uid":170929,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"焦慮症+社交恐懼症撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次遊行集會好撚多人都好撚驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"