㗎<br />\n<br />\n想知嘅話我可以再提供多少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"我出左院都有睇中醫，但佢只係話我陰虛內熱<br />\n叫我飲啲花旗參水，我本身已經頭暈仲要我飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:22:55.000Z","msg":"條友冇料，因為我係久病成醫 我睇好多中醫㗎！<br />\n初起嘅小小情緒困擾同埋肝鬱係一定可以醫到㗎。你先試吓<br />\n玫瑰焗水先，每日都可以飲有M都可以，每日一杯嘅話唔會寒又唔會熱！<br />\n<br />\n我係養生撚嚟 嘅仲有其他養生疏肝解鬱嘅配方但你可以先試左玫瑰先💪🏻"},{"pid":"d72600a37d2814e32b2bb82a9048245bc5b05339","tid":1514010,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a423f0c4e96295ce85e14f5b72e8c85ada87a977","tid":1514010,"uid":206417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:26:53.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲打知道<br />\n食左2-3年名叫venlafaxine既抗焦慮藥 , 突然停藥, 會點?<br />\n急問"},{"pid":"7f31c1258b01e83ed3f0568fbf5e790dd5a8cb8e","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"剛剛先發現到醫院幫我按排既係臨床心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問係咪唔會有藥食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8590ed8563dfc345d72eade4563d3f6e7b9ddc68","tid":1514010,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"焦慮symptoms here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以去睇下有個網叫<span style=\"color: orange;\">心導遊</span>  有個認知行為訓練都有用"},{"pid":"739d09f57318aafb0db6217bbd2deeb38b217f4a","tid":1514010,"uid":159642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f31c1258b01e83ed3f0568fbf5e790dd5a8cb8e","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"剛剛先發現到醫院幫我按排既係臨床心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問係咪唔會有藥食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:13:07.0