ab86188f8ccc03db3cf9bd4590","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"739d09f57318aafb0db6217bbd2deeb38b217f4a","tid":1514010,"uid":159642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f31c1258b01e83ed3f0568fbf5e790dd5a8cb8e","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"剛剛先發現到醫院幫我按排既係臨床心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問係咪唔會有藥食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"如果真係急需要藥可以出去睇私家情緒病醫生 佢會開著藥比你食先<br />\n雖然有啲貴 但等啲政府醫生處理情緒病都唔知要等到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:09:13.000Z","msg":"我諗真係需要，我每日都keep住頭重頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93f8bda66448c86417a031cb73ab7575850e0eb","tid":1514010,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3a5142a5aedf1be0851f61e02cbbfe981438a6","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"八月頭突然係街心跳快到170幾<br />\n幾乎暈低，入院檢查晒話冇事住左三日就放左我出院<br />\n第四日食晏個又突然跳到160幾又送返入廠<br />\n最終係醫院訓左4,5日先有個臨床心理醫生見我<br />\n話我有恐慌症同焦慮症<br />\n長期工作壓力而成，最近兩個月又不段睇新聞，發過一次夢。<br />\n醫院個度要排到9月中先有醫生睇，現在都係無藥食每日都keep頭重重，個人浮下浮下咁。<br />\n想睇下有冇巴絲同樣有衣個病，同醫治情況係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪第一次見醫生已經會開藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲係衣段時間記得都搵野放鬆下自己，千祈唔好迫得自己太緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=79d3769c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"44d3e06a3680482b0ff55dd1ba08fdd8eb2b00fc","tid":1514010,"uid":296077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845ded8f2643435516be8af3302ceed4720c07de","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c61e32250a2ed918048bb22e95b8120b627d766","tid":1514010,"uid":296077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:57:59.000Z","msg":"恐慌+燥鬰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食年幾藥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"巴打係睇政府定私家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"海外撚&hellip;&hellip;聽講香港睇好貴 但我呢邊批啲藥既藥力無香港咁勁（有fd 係香港拎藥過黎食 佢食呢邊啲藥無用）<br />\n<br />\n試過食普通藥都冇用 衝去拎緊急用 醫生都話最好就唔好食咁多緊急既&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n一開始食副作用超勁 好似肉體同精神分離咁 呆呆滯滯 過左一個月就無副作用了<br />\n<br />\n我第一時係同班fd 講我有呢啲病 佢地都好support 我同叫我有咩事就同佢地講<br />\n<br />\n不過香港發生咁多野睇到個人又好鬰 太擔心又會panic attack 所以有時上少啲fb 連登平靜下好啲"},{"pid":"ecbd4fb9ad88a44b4ac453947d5fcddac3dc8d2c","tid":1514010,"uid":313870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b134f419eba6f1fcfe62f13b4c47ef5f9d11ca1","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44829b3a7cee2aead5f7a7bfbda6d0dcb45cb4a8","tid":1514010,"uid":313870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:12:52.000Z","msg":"以前試過Panic attack入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屋企人只係覺得我杞人憂天咁 擔心埋啲無謂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上我係連出街都覺得好驚個啲 上到地鐵又覺得比人望住 基本上自己出街就好驚好驚 會瘋狂手震"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"咁絲打現在點 有冇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"冇啊 之前試下同屋企人講佢地都只係覺得我自己諗多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />耐左就冇左睇醫生呢個念頭"},{"pid":"d4d76494855b2c40063ee0c9499a999f8d47db8a","tid":1514010,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcdfd098426f40fdf95c596517ccd11359ac151d","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72600a37d2814e32b2bb82a9048245bc5b05339","tid":1514010,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02c8ef344265ba4675dd551e3e146a80f934bbd","tid":1514010,"uid":71216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520fe71189be13f4e61f7b84cec9f7e457ac5965","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bfb59b65c3aa480d74f6be0e6abef18cd13a6f","tid":1514010,"uid":159642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"520fe71189be13f4e61f7b84cec9f7e457ac5965","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"撐住呀巴打<br />\n因為你係驚自己病發所以先會心跳快 越心跳快就越驚病發 最後會去到真係病發 惡性循環黎<br />\n要記住自己其實好健康 只不過係情緒病令到你咁 而恐慌症係唔會傷害到你半條毛髮<br />\n加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024a