"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都要逼住自己出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次一路胃痛、作嘔咁行<br />\n要做好多心理準備先出到去<br />\n然後逼得多發現自己無咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c090fdd784c66648c3ea4f20171f54c6cf6975","tid":1514010,"uid":73284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"我而家就係訓唔到好似又有d發作<br />\n<br />\n近呢個禮拜d新聞真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3bc9d20747c63c19984b831ff211df61ad9f70","tid":1514010,"uid":258683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3814a6f2008f51fbc458e217faf2c5f65fb864f1","tid":1514010,"uid":170929,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"焦慮症+社交恐懼症撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次遊行集會好撚多人都好撚驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都要逼住自己出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:35:08.000Z","msg":"屌 我懷疑自己都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行還好 集會停係一個地方就好柒怯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74f90ed022be231395c36d643397ba8939291c3","tid":1514010,"uid":305335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3a5142a5aedf1be0851f61e02cbbfe981438a6","tid":1514010,"uid":19399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"八月頭突然係街心跳快到170幾<br />\n幾乎暈低，入院檢查晒話冇事住左三日就放左我出院<br />\n第四日食晏個又突然跳到160幾又送返入廠<br />\n最終係醫院訓左4,5日先有個臨床心理醫生見我<br />\n話我有恐慌症同焦慮症<br />\n長期工作壓力而成，最近兩個月又不段睇新聞，發過一次夢。<br />\n醫院個度要排到9月中先有醫生睇，現在都係無藥食每日都keep頭重重，個人浮下浮下咁。<br />\n想睇下有冇巴絲同樣有衣個病，同醫治情況係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪第一次見醫生已經會開藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲係衣段時間記得都搵野放鬆下自己，千祈唔好迫得自己太緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T19:15:48.000Z","msg":"有，有時嚴重到手震得好嚴重 心慌心怯 焦慮 莫名精神緊張 頭暈 企唔穩 雙眼試過持續分幾鐘到發黑（兩眼黑色一片咩都睇唔到，好似失明咁款），好似就暈墜地咁款"},{"pid":"5cc519cb8ab3ffc8d4c9f87afbeb7bc90dad1d2b","tid":1514010,"uid":30207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"一個月前試過心口痛，去急症抽血，照x光，做2次心電圖都冇事，之後成個月都好驚有事，尋晚夜晚突然心口又刺痛，去再照定睇精神科好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5c76bbdaafe0de937823e45b498d26f3ed8485","tid":1514010,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"睇政府要轉介信？"},{"pid":"3a391c5f8fba85f134a9881a7fb2ce31224fd0bc","tid":1514010,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cc519cb8ab3ffc8d4c9f87afbeb7bc90dad1d2b","tid":1514010,"uid":30207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"一個月前試過心口痛，去急症抽血，照x光，做2次心電圖都冇事，之後成個月都好驚有事，尋晚夜晚突然心口又刺痛，去再照定睇精神科好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"公立醫院？"},{"pid":"e51b6e0647c46a68805d4af07c74b8c359cd49ba","tid":1514010,"uid":30207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a391c5f8fba85f134a9881a7fb2ce31224fd0bc","tid":1514010,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cc519cb8ab3ffc8d4c9f87afbeb7bc90dad1d2b","tid":1514010,"uid":30207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"一個月前試過心口痛，去急症抽血，照x光，做2次心電圖都冇事，之後成個月都好驚有事，尋晚夜晚突然心口又刺痛，去再照定睇精神科好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:10:44.0